Argus: Active pipeline needs attention.
Pipeline: {{.Issue.PipelineID}} | Workflow: {{.Issue.WorkflowID}}

Issue: {{.Issue.Issue}}

Guide the user with a concise choice set before taking action:
1. Investigate first with `{{.Issue.InvestigateCommand}}` to {{.Issue.InvestigateGuidance}}.
2. Cancel the broken pipeline with `argus workflow cancel`.
3. Snooze this pipeline for the current session with `argus workflow snooze --session {{.Issue.SessionID}}` and continue the current task.

Prefer cancel when the user wants to get unstuck quickly. Prefer investigate first when they want to understand the problem before changing state.
